shanghai
Homonym Number: 1
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a child's catapult [from Scottish dialect shangy, a stick split at one end for putting on a dog's tail, a variant of Gaelic seangan]
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
